    "Fig. 7 shows the evolution of ε 99 (n) as a function of the number of scenarios, together with the convergence threshold.",
    "As the number of simulations increases, the nearest-neighbor distance decreases approximately monotonically, indicating progressively finer resolution of the short-circuit current distribution.",
    "The resolution criterion (??)",
